{"tid":2206051,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《惡靈勢力 2（Left 4 Dead 2）》宣布將於 24 日更新最新版本《最後一刻》","createTime":"2020-09-17T08:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T14:24:32.000Z","uid":250308,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"42274807926abda19c50a99cb5f41aa5089add7a","tid":2206051,"uid":250308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T08:49:21.000Z","msg":"Valve 旗下著名的恐怖射擊遊戲《惡靈勢力 2（Left 4 Dead 2）》時隔許久，終於將於 9 月 24 日更新最新版本《惡靈勢力 2：最後一刻（Left 4 Dead 2：The Last Stand）》，官方今日同步公開了預告影片。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n　　《最後一刻》原本是《惡靈勢力》一代中生存模式的燈塔地圖，後來由粉絲製作成為二代劇情地圖，而 Valve 後來決定接納這個創作加以扶正、正式更新到遊戲中，《惡靈勢力 2：最後一刻》由 30 多名社群玩家與 Valve 的《戰慄時空：艾莉克絲》研發成員共同合作，歷經 11 個月的時間進行研發。<br />\n <br />\n　　研發成員 JAiZ 今日透過 Youtube 宣布了《惡靈勢力 2：最後一刻》的更新日期與相關內容，包括最後一刻戰役、26 張新生存地圖、30 個全新成就、4 張清道夫模式地圖、2 種全新近戰武器、L4D1 感染者、新的角色動畫、增強 PVP、UI 進化等：<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n　　《惡靈勢力 2：最後一刻》預定 24 日正式更新。<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=203332\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fgnn%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D203332&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOP5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=69a5c508\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=203332</a>"},{"pid":"8ea7c89e7f586c7e2b0c46a1e86f246221a8ed93","tid":2206051,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T08:52:47.000Z","msg":"Bill<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785d08825aa03423bf4d1abd9935e4de44e420e3","tid":2206051,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T08:53:29.000Z","msg":"6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d39f23c9176b6b04c29747c8896e806e0e55689","tid":2206051,"uid":68689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T08:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/3LWBQD3EfqU/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.y